Module kbaldr2.main
Package kbaldr2.model

Class DataCache

java.lang.Object
kbaldr2.model.DataCache
Direct Known Subclasses:
Appointment, Contact, Customer, Location, User
public abstract class DataCache extends Object
Represents an abstract DataCache class that stores the data for appointments, customers, users, contacts, and locations.
